---
import AppPageLayout from "../../layouts/AppPageLayout.astro";
import { Header } from "../../app/components/Header";
import { Footer } from "../../app/components/Footer";
---

<AppPageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Pokedoku Helper and Pokedoku Details"
  description="Privacy policy for the Pokedoku Helper website and Pokedoku Details Devvit app."
  path="/privacy-policy/"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden p-5">
    <Header
      title="Pokedoku Helper"
      subtitle="Legal information"
      currentPage="home"
      client:load
    />

    <main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--bg)] p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8">
        <h1 class="m-0 text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--text-h)]">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text)]">Last updated: May 7, 2026</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-h)]">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-[var(--text)]">Pokedoku Helper (website) and Pokedoku Details (Devvit app) do not require account registration. We may collect limited technical data such as page views, app interactions, and device or browser information to understand usage.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-h)]">How We Use Information</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-[var(--text)]">We use collected information to maintain, improve, and monitor the performance of both the website and Devvit app, and to understand which features are most useful to users.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-h)]">Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-[var(--text)]">The website and Devvit app may use privacy-friendly analytics and similar technologies. These tools help us measure usage and improve user experience.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-h)]">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-[var(--text)]">Our services may link to third-party services (for example, Pokedoku, Reddit, and GitHub). Their privacy practices are governed by their own policies.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-h)]">Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-[var(--text)]">We do not sell your personal information. We only share data when required to operate these services (such as analytics providers and platform infrastructure) or when legally required.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-h)]">Policy Updates</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-[var(--text)]">We may update this policy over time. Any updates will be posted on this page and reflected in the "Last updated" date.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-h)]">Contact</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-[var(--text)]">If you have privacy questions, please open an issue at <a class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/jlast/pokedoku-solver/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/jlast/pokedoku-solver/issues</a>.</p>
      </article>
    </main>

    <Footer client:load />
  </div>
</AppPageLayout>
